<template>
  <v-card
      dark
  >
    <v-img
        height="55vh"
        src="https://unsplash.com/photos/nF8xhLMmg0c/download?ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MXxhbGx8fHx8fHx8fHwxNjcxODk0NDk2&force=true&w=640"
    >

      <v-card-title>Enter any public lobby and start chatting</v-card-title>

      <v-divider></v-divider>

      <v-card-actions class="pb-4">
        <v-btn
            light
            @click="reserve"
        >
          Create Room
        </v-btn>
      </v-card-actions>
    </v-img>
  </v-card>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: 'PublicLobbiesCard',
  data: () => ({
    loading: false,
    selection: 1,
  }),

  methods: {
    reserve () {
      this.loading = true

      setTimeout(() => (this.loading = false), 2000)
    },
  },
}
</script>
